# Inertia + React/Vue Rules

## Inertia Overview
Inertia bridges Laravel routes/controllers to JS frontends like React/Vue without separate API layers. :contentReference[oaicite:5]{index=5}

## Folder Structure
- resources/js/pages/ — Inertia pages
- resources/js/components/ — UI components

## Rules
- Controllers return Inertia::render(…) with data.
- Data passed to frontend should be minimal and serialized.